# 2026-05-11 audit-transparency pass (Aether + Andrew, addressing
# Grok's Schneier finding on gitignored-folders-escaping-audit):
# on the EXPERIMENTAL repo, agent definitions are part of the lived
# substrate that audit-vantage needs read access to. The main
# DivineOS template keeps these ignored (clean-slate for fresh
# clones). Here, .claude/agents/ is tracked. Agent-memory runtime
# state stays ignored because it's noisy and regenerable.
.claude/agent-memory/

