/family/family.db-shm
/family/family.db-wal
/family/*_ledger.db
/family/*_ledger.db-shm
/family/*_ledger.db-wal

# Canonical-substrate marker — opt-in flag the operator places at the
# parent repo root to indicate "this is a continuous Aether substrate;
# worktrees should share my event ledger." When absent (default for
# fresh template clones), each worktree gets its own ledger — correct
# for new agents bootstrapping continuity. When present, worktree
# sessions inherit the parent's accumulated history. Resolution logic
# in core/_ledger_base.py:_get_db_path. Andrew's workspace has it;
# the published template does not.
/.divineos_canonical

